dc_title_s: Roads and ROW St. Croix County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent roads and Right of Ways (ROW) for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'St_Croix_Roads_ROW_2018.gdb'. [The areas of land that are managed for the real estate tax system, these may be multipart polygons, all have a unique tax key number.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://sccgis-scccdd.opendata.arcgis.com/
